summary: YoYoCoin - YOYO is a new coin project focused on creating a fun and rewarding experience for its community. The project aims to educate newcomers in the crypto space and provide benefits to its holders and investors. The YoYoNomics of the project include a total supply of 10,000,000,000 YOYO, with 10% allocated to the Dev Team and 90% to Pre-Sale/Liquidity. The project also outlines a 7% transaction fee distribution, with 4% going to Holders and 3% to Auto Liquidity. The roadmap includes milestones such as website creation, social media outreach, NFT launches, and partnerships with real-world businesses.
